tton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526095\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 16, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bko1665702974302.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bko1665702974302.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bko1665702974302.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bko1665702974302\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Upgrade to Row-Level, Data Pages, and All Pages Locking\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"bko1665702974302__context_w3906ab1b5b1_w3907ab1b5_w3908ab1\">\n<div class=\"div context\" id=\"bko1665702974302__topic_d61352e1_d61353e1_d61354e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bko1665702974302__p_d61355e1_d61356e1_d61357e1\">To use row-level, data pages, or all pages locking, do the following:</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step\" id=\"bko1665702974302__li_d26972e1_d26973e1_d26974e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Add the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">row level locks</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">datapages locking</span>, or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">allpages locking</span> connector options to your assignment file.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"bko1665702974302__li_d26975e1_d26976e1_d26977e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Add the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">upgrade locks</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">upgrade dpl</span>, or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">upgrade apl</span> connector option to your assignment file, for row-level locking, data pages locking, and all pages locking, respectively.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"bko1665702974302__li_d26978e1_d26979e1_d26980e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Run the Create Table facility on all modeled database entities.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"bko1665702974302__li_d26981e1_d26982e1_d26983e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Run the generated SQL scripts.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"bko1665702974302__li_d26984e1_d26985e1_d26986e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Remove the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">upgrade locks</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">upgrade dpl</span>, or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">upgrade apl</span> connector option from your assignment file.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"bko1665702974302__li_d26987e1_d26988e1_d26989e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Stop and restart the Sybase SQL Server.\n </span>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vxw1665702686009.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>row level locks</a><p>Create tables with row level locking.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/stv1665702734543.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>datapages locking</a><p>Create tables with data pages locking.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iwb1665702734332.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>allpages locking</a><p>Create tables with all pages locking.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bhk1665702968969.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>upgrade locks</a><p>Upgrade locking for existing tables to data pages, all pages, or row-level locking.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526095\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526095\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Upgrade to Row-Level, Data Pages, and All Pages Locking Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 16, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Upgrade to Row-Level, Data Pages, and All Pages Locking To use row-level, data pages, or all pages locking, do the following: Add the row level locks , datapages locking , or allpages locking connector options to your assignment file. Add the upgrade locks , upgrade dpl , or upgrade apl connector option to your assignment file, for row-level locking, data pages locking, and all pages locking, respectively. Run the Create Table facility on all modeled database entities. Run the generated SQL scripts. Remove the upgrade locks , upgrade dpl , or upgrade apl connector option from your assignment file. Stop and restart the Sybase SQL Server. Related Links row level locks Create tables with row level locking. datapages locking Create tables with data pages locking. allpages locking Create tables with all pages locking. upgrade locks Upgrade locking for existing tables to data pages, all pages, or row-level locking. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}